        <abstract> 
<p>Wants to amend request [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">2946</hi>] if DO wants to try carbonate of ammonia experiment. Put third drop on midrib of leaf [of <hi rend="italic">Dionaea</hi>] or inside upper side.</p>  
<p>Sorry DO already has <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. Would he like Journal of Travels [<hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>]?</p> 
